/**
 * Minimal internal i18n for UI chrome only (no library).
 *
 * Scope: buttons, labels, headings, helper text, empty states, navigation,
 * static status copy. It deliberately does NOT cover the live transcript, user
 * speech, AI tutor replies, or grading/analysis bodies generated by the backend
 * — LUVE stays an English speaking-practice app, so practice content remains in
 * its original language.
 *
 * `en` is the source of truth for the key set; `vi` is typed to it, so a missing
 * Vietnamese key is a compile error. `translate` falls back to English, then to
 * the raw key, and supports simple `{name}` placeholder substitution.
 */
